  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个物流系统的流程图，核心是车队管理模块。我想从Logistics_FleetManagement开始，它要触发获取运单号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，FleetManagement是起点。那它和TrackingNumber之间的动作是什么？是\"获取运单号\"还是\"分配运单号\"？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "用\"Get money\"吧，这是我们内部术语，表示确认费用后获取运单号。然后TrackingNumber要进入配送路由的判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把TrackingNumber连接到配送路由判断节点。这个菱形节点是Logistics_DeliveryRoute，接下来它要分支对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，DeliveryRoute要分出三条线。第一条到Logistics_Warehouse，标记为\"One\"，表示需要入库的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "第一条分支画好了，Warehouse是矩形节点。第二条分支呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二条标记\"Two\"，指向另一个Logistics_DeliveryRoute节点，这是中转路由的情况。第三条标记\"Three\"，回到Logistics_TrackingNumber，表示需要重新生成运单号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，第二条分支的终点也叫Logistics_DeliveryRoute？这和判断节点同名，不会混淆吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，业务上就是这么命名的。判断节点是路由决策，第二个DeliveryRoute是具体的中转路由执行模块。请按这个来画。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，第二条分支已添加。现在画第三条分支\"Three\"回到TrackingNumber。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，让我看一下整体结构。FleetManagement到TrackingNumber的箭头标签确认是\"Get money\"吗？我想再检查一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，箭头标签是\"Get money\"。整个流程是：FleetManagement --|Get money|-- TrackingNumber -- DeliveryRoute判断 -- 三条分支。需要调整吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这个结构正确。三条分支分别对应入库、中转路由、重新生成运单号，覆盖了我们的主要业务场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
